source.name: Fisheries One Stop Shop (FOSS)
source.description: An online query tool for accessing the most current and comprehensive national summary statistics on U.S. commercial and recreational fisheries landings. The FOSS query tool allows scientists, managers, and the public to query non-confidential commercial and recreational fisheries landings  (three or more vessels or companies) for U.S. vessels in both domestic and foreign ports, as well as for recreational shore anglers.
